{"tid":1108140,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［打手］幾個月前買左Sofina枝土台美容液","createTime":"2019-04-15T17:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T10:58:32.000Z","uid":138731,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c13507131dd57026f97838d25d8f680acc2505f6","tid":1108140,"uid":138731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"本身我嘴既周圍係成日爛 下巴勁多暗瘡<br />\n嘴脣有一排又係咁生唇瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用靚啲既牌子洗面 落妝 用鎮靜作用既toner敷都無用<br />\n嗰排真係覺得自己好撚樣衰<br />\n啲瘡用遮瑕都遮唔住 好快甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著係Sofina買base嗰陣諗住試下枝肌底精華<br />\n開頭用無咩感覺 但耐左開始發現我明明每日都3-4點先訓<br />\n有時係攰到帶妝訓著左 再半夜起身洗<br />\n我塊面居然少左粒粒 嘴周都無再爛 唇瘡係就黎發嗰陣就自己消左<br />\n我呢個垃圾作息 又瘋狂飲凍野 吹冷氣 夜訓 亂食野<br />\n就算有暗瘡都三兩日就消<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我早幾個月明明唔係咁<br />\n我懷疑緊係咪呢枝野有用<br />\n<br />\n到底真係佢啲乜柒納米科技有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定佢落啲左好勁既化學野乸到我皮膚短暫地好 但一唔用佢就會爛面？<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔敢停用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVKQfDK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVKQfDK.png&h=40504504&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07c4edaa825edd9958b8540c695adbbfa5f77885","tid":1108140,"uid":138731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T01:20:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10354a49db011502c700948a6f937de20187fbe","tid":1108140,"uid":138731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人都有用"},{"pid":"7ec0f57d1bd10aee25e836f1cc2151e333ce68af","tid":1108140,"uid":83682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"